ZOMBIE-NET
----------



                  .....                                                  
                 C C  /                                                  
                /<   /     Zombie-Net is a self replicating  
 ___ __________/_#__=o     local area network that allows 
/(- /(\_\________   \      you to build your own internet.
\ ) \ )_      \o     \       
/|\ /|\       |'     |                 
              |     _|     Use whenever you have a network
              /o   __\     but lack access to the interwebs.
             / '     |                        
            / /      |                                                   
           /_/\______|     Just run ~$ node zombie-net.js
          (   _(    <                                                    
           \    \    \                                                   
